@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About";
}

<div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded shadow-sm">

        <h1 class="mb-4">About Fox Shelter 🦊</h1>

        <p class="lead">
            Fox Shelter is a community-driven platform focused on protecting foxes affected by urban expansion.
        </p>

        <p>
            As cities continue to grow, natural habitats are being reduced or destroyed, forcing wild animals like foxes to adapt to unsafe urban environments. This often leads to road accidents, lack of food, and conflicts with humans or domestic animals.
        </p>

        <p>
            The purpose of this application is to create awareness and provide support for these animals. Through Fox Shelter, users can explore rescued foxes, learn about their stories, and see where they were found. The platform also highlights areas where fox activity is higher, helping to identify zones that may need protection in the future.
        </p>

        <p>
            Members of the community can share their experiences, report cases where foxes might be in danger, and contribute to a growing network of people who care about wildlife safety.
        </p>

        <p class="fw-bold text-center mt-4">
            “NO CONCRETE SLOP IN THIS DEN”
        </p>

    </div>
</div>